Alberta Nelson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alberta_Nelson 0 Alberta Nelson (August 14, 1937 – April 29, 2006) was an American television and film actress. After several dramatic parts in television in the early 1960s, she made five guest appearances on The Andy Griffith Show.
